{"tid":1473130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"總結三次天水圍發夢見聞","createTime":"2019-08-14T18:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T18:33:05.000Z","uid":176799,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6c00943ca0f017915ce5213468dd21a0c51feeb0","tid":1473130,"uid":176799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:12:19.000Z","msg":"天水圍手足多勇武就大家都知<br />\n基本上次次都街坊為主 個個踢拖咁樣<br />\n但就算<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再勇都好 受傷始終都係我哋洩底</span></span><br />\n大家至少都眼罩豬嘴好唔好？<br />\n乜都冇都唔緊要 帶返個口罩着條長褲好難咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜嘢裝備都冇仲係咁挑釁啲狗<br />\n口罩又唔帶喺度食住支煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋出來跑唔切就一定有人賴嘢<br />\n最慘嘅係有手足提醒反而俾人屌係唔係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大佬上次天水圍個女仔大家有眼見<br />\n着到背心短裙咁樣就算唔俾狗搞 出蛋你都死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發夢最基本嘅條件 係保護自己 至少唔使拖累他人<br />\n兩個幾月啦<span style=\"font-size: large;\"> 唔好再重複悲劇 醒下啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd94eb6f44cb0e6e3ae9e6176dcea4930c27e0d","tid":1473130,"uid":176799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:13:23.000Z","msg":"大家發夢 就算氣氛有幾歡樂都要有警覺性啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd2e187924fd6d507a1eb0a0cad51bca28eed77","tid":1473130,"uid":176799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:14:15.000Z","msg":"每次俾人捉幾個 打傷幾個 我哋挨唔到好耐嘅咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da69b5fa79e1a4a29fdccab7539d5512b71d66d8","tid":1473130,"uid":176799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:16:58.000Z","msg":"唔好諗住自己係街坊好快返到屋企<br />\n大安旨意乜都唔帶 啲狗冇性 佢唔會理乜身份<br />\n無論發夢去任何地方都好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保護自己，帶齊裝備，有警覺性</span></span>"},{"pid":"a0f3be2ce411ed24e9fc708230dde185e63aa252","tid":1473130,"uid":149435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:17:03.000Z","msg":"認同 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家要<span style=\"color: red;\">不受傷不被捕</span><br />\n每次都應該要有返警戒心<br />\n經過咁多次唔係唔知天水圍<br />\n啲狗有幾賤 一落車就衝埋嚟拉理得你係咪街坊"},{"pid":"af218077c65418ce97d78215ab24130947d5280c","tid":1473130,"uid":176799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0f3be2ce411ed24e9fc708230dde185e63aa252","tid":1473130,"uid":149435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:17:03.000Z","msg":"認同 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家要<span style=\"color: red;\">不受傷不被捕</span><br />\n每次都應該要有返警戒心<br />\n經過咁多次唔係唔知天水圍<br />\n啲狗有幾賤 一落車就衝埋嚟拉理得你係咪街坊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:19:03.000Z","msg":"啱啱有豬嘴嘅一隻手數晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出咗藍旗都仲喺度喧鬧唔識死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺度話要出催淚彈先肯走 點知行落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689bb3e196f5c7082d5d59aacc00c99acc818816","tid":1473130,"uid":180204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:19:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c7fa0a58f00c346b3db63aeba2f6783493a5c8","tid":1473130,"uid":176799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"689bb3e196f5c7082d5d59aacc00c99acc818816","tid":1473130,"uid":180204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:19:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:21:44.000Z","msg":"唔係割 但係現場太多小朋友<br />\n其實有一段時間大家都阻止人照laser<br />\n只不過燒晒衣紙之後冇嘢做一發不可收拾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw 代我地同兩老講聲對唔住嚇親佢<img src=\"/a